Develop and demonstrate a XHTML document that illustrates the use external style sheet, 
ordered list, table, borders, padding, color, and the <span> tag


<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <title>External Style Sheet Example</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css" />
</head>

<body>

<h2>Programming Languages</h2>

<ol>
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>Java</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>C++</li>
</ol>

<h2>Student Details</h2>

<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Course</th>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Rahul</td>
        <td>BCA</td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Anita</td>
        <td>B.Tech</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>
    <span>HTML</span> is used to create web pages.
</p>

</body>
</html>










body{
    font-family: Arial;
    background-color: lightyellow;
}

h2{
    color: blue;
}

table{
    border: 2px solid black;
    border-collapse: collapse;
}

th, td{
    border: 1px solid black;
    padding: 10px;
}

span{
    color: red;
    font-weight: bold;
}
